    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi everyone! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape, ready to hit the road with you! It drives smoothly and has been really well-cared for over the years. It's the perfect fit for someone who wants a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to go. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
