    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving masterpiece. Powered by the S54B32 inline-six, it features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for precise timing across the powerband. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts flawlessly, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings have been addressed. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, and the hydraulic steering remains sharp and communicative. This is an excellent driver's car that balances raw performance with refined engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
