    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a reliable ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next owner! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty handles perfectly and looks great doing it. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to a great home. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 32000.0,
