      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and the Variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. The chassis dynamics are supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing three-stage adjustment of the MacPherson strut and five-link rear suspension geometry. Recent technical service includes proactive rod bearing replacement and refreshed throttle actuators, ensuring the high-pressure VANOS system and valvetrain maintain peak volumetric efficiency. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved performance machine, the subframe remains structurally sound and the bushings provide precise tactile feedback. A mechanically sorted specimen ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
